# The generated Convex api/types ARE committed: CI has no Convex deployment, so
# it cannot run `convex codegen`, and apps/app imports `../convex/_generated/api`
# — without these files the app typecheck fails. Regenerate with
# `pnpm convex:codegen` after changing convex functions or the schema.
